dct_title_s: General highway and transportation map of Kosciusko County, Indiana
dct_description_sm: "State roads revised to January 1, 1949." "1937." "Data obtained from State-wide Highway Planning Survey. Includes location map and chart of "Culture in unincorporated places." Supplementary sheet includes maps of Lake Wawasee, Tippecanoe Lake, Webster Lake, and a group of Bantam Lake, Irish Lake, Mable Lake, Plew Lake, Kuhn Lake, Barbee Lake, Hammon Lake, and Heron Lake. "49, 49A (supplementary sheet)."
Imprint: [Indianapolis?] : State Highway Commission of Indiana, 1949.
Scale: 1:130,000; Dimensions: 52 x 44 cm + supplementary sheet (4 maps on 1 sheet, sheet 44 x 52 cm)
